---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Subheading from "../components/Subheading.astro";
import Paragraph from "../components/Paragraph.astro";
---
<Layout>
  <Section id="hero" classList="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-36 px-4">
		<Header>
			Now
		</Header>
		<Subheading classList={'max-w-2xl mt-6'}>
      This is my now page, and shows what I am focusing on right now.
		</Subheading>
	</Section>

  <Section id="about" classList="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-36 px-4">
    <article class="prose lg:prose-xl max-w-7xl dark:text-gray-50 leading-7 tracking-wide">
      <Paragraph>
        As part of the dynamic team at <a href="https://www.juststeveking.uk/now/undefined?utm_campaign=juststeveking-website&utm_source=juststeveking&utm_medium=textlink&utm_term=social+share">Treblle</a>, I'm deeply immersed in enhancing our platform and SDKs. My focus is on fostering API excellence within the PHP community, guiding our growth through innovative approaches and developer advocacy.
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph>
        My passion for teaching and sharing knowledge continues to thrive. Each week, I contribute tutorials to <a href="https://laravel-news.com/?utm_campaign=juststeveking-website&utm_source=juststeveking&utm_medium=textlink&utm_term=social+share">Laravel News</a>, where I delve into various aspects of Laravel, aiming to ensure technical accuracy and applicability. At <a href="https://phparch.com/?utm_campaign=juststeveking-website&utm_source=juststeveking&utm_medium=textlink&utm_term=social+share">php[architect]</a>, I explore more advanced topics, providing in-depth insights into PHP development.
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph>
        I'm actively engaged in speaking at various conferences, sharing my expertise and experiences in software development. These events are a fantastic opportunity to connect with the community, exchange ideas, and stay abreast of the latest industry trends.
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph>
        Join me on my YouTube channel, where I host live streams, offering real-time tutorials, Q&A sessions, and deep dives into Laravel and PHP. It's a platform where I connect with my audience, share my screen, and code live, tackling real-world problems.
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph>
        The open-source community is where I give back, contributing to various projects. I'm committed to developing tools and solutions that benefit developers worldwide, fostering a culture of collaboration and innovation.
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph>
        Stay tuned for more updates and feel free to connect with me on my social channels for the latest insights and happenings in my professional journey.
      </Paragraph>
      <Paragraph>
        Learn more about <a href="https://nownownow.com/about?utm_campaign=juststeveking-website&utm_source=juststeveking&utm_medium=textlink&utm_term=social+share">now pages</a>, and what they are.
      </Paragraph>
    </article>
  </Section>
</Layout>